This paper is primarily focused on the performance analysis of SQL-on-Hadoop systems for data analytics, which falls under the database (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), and data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also discusses the design decisions and implementation details of the systems, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
